            "title": "Caliway Selected to Present Preclinical Data on CBL-514 in Combination with GLP-1R Therapy at ECO 2026",
            "id": "a9b0da1e-1b16-4983-be55-5d5b413bdfb5",
            "description": "Research findings on the potential fat reduction drug candidate CBL-514 by Caliway, when used alongside weight-loss therapies based on GLP-1R, have been chosen for oral presentation at the European Congress on Obesity (ECO 2026). Arya M. Sharma, MD, from Caliway will be presenting these preclinical data during the event. The combination of CBL-514 and GLP-1R therapies is showing promise in addressing weight-related concerns. This presentation at ECO 2026 signifies a significant step in the development of potential treatments, and it highlights the growing interest in innovative weight-loss approaches.",
